snippet.title: Gamecube Trailer: 1080 Avalanche
snippet.description:
I'm got some more old trailers to go up this week. Just a little change of pace while I work on some things. First up, the second trailer, at least in uploading order for me, of 1080 Avalanche. I liked this one just because it reminds me of attitude games, I miss them.
